OL,6,F"I sometimes feel loathed and
OL,7,Funwelcome just walking through the
OL,8,Fstreets of London ` not because of
OL,9,Fanything I've done, but simply because
OL,10,Fof who I am ` a Muslim woman."
OL,12,FThe poll follows a warning earlier
OL,13,Fthis year from Tell Mama, an
OL,14,Forganisation that monitors anti-Muslim
OL,15,Fhate, which reported that anti-Muslim
OL,16,Fhate in the UK had reached record
OL,17,Flevels.
