OL,6,FTell Mama recorded 6,313 incidents of
OL,7,Fanti-Muslim hate in 2024, representing
OL,8,Fa 43% increase on the previous year.
OL,9,FOf those, 5,837 were verified by the
OL,10,Forganisation.
OL,12,FIts Director, Iman Atta, said the
OL,13,Ffindings of the poll, along with Tell
OL,14,FMama's own data, highlighted the
OL,15,Fgrowing problem of Islamophobia and
OL,16,Fits influence on daily decision-making
OL,17,Ffor British Muslims.
