OL,6,F"This sense of a collective self-
OL,7,Fenforced sense of restraint of what
OL,8,Fthey can do and when they can go out
OL,9,Fis troubling since it has mental and
OL,10,Femotional impacts, as well as economic
OL,11,Fimpacts that are acutely felt by
OL,12,FBritish Muslim women," Iman Atta said.
OL,14,FMore than a quarter of Muslims
OL,15,Fsurveyed said they had stopped using
OL,16,Fsocial media entirely as a result of
OL,17,Fthe abuse and harmful content they had
OL,18,Fencountered online.
