OL,6,FExperts say this been driven by
OL,7,Fchanges to social media algorithms,
OL,8,Fthe Southport murders last July and
OL,9,Fthe Israel-Gaza conflict.
OL,11,FTufail Hussain, UK Director of Islamic
OL,12,FRelief, which commissioned the poll,
OL,13,Fsaid that too many people were
OL,14,Fincreasingly feeling emboldened to
OL,15,Fpost harmful content and that more
OL,16,Fneeded to be done to protect minority
OL,17,Fcommunities.
