OL,6,F"This survey is a wake-up call for the
OL,7,FUK government to do everything it can
OL,8,Fdo make the Muslim community safe and
OL,9,Ffor tech companies to tackle hate
OL,10,Fspeech and protect users online. We
OL,11,Fcannot tolerate abuse, harassment, or
OL,12,Fdiscrimination based on religion."
OL,14,FDr Naomi Green, Assistant Secretary
OL,15,FGeneral of the Muslim Council of
OL,16,FBritain, said the findings were "more
OL,17,Fevidence of the mainstreaming of
OL,18,FIslamophobia".
